Table(
    {
        EventTitle : "Text" , 
        ID:1,
        EventDescription : "Text" , 
        EventDate : "2025-12-25" , 
        EventColor: "#f65810" , 
        EventPlan : 100 , 
        EventActual : 80 , 
        EventDateStart : "2025-12-24" , 
        EventDateEnd : "2025-12-26" 
    }
)

If( Or( IsBlank(_comp_selected_year) , IsBlank(_comp_selected_month)), 
Parent.Height - Self.Y*2 ,
Parent.Height/10*1 )

If( IsBlank(_comp_selected_month) , 0 ,
If( IsBlank(_comp_selected_year) , 
Parent.Width , 
Parent.Width/4
))

If( Month(ThisItem.Value) <> Month(comp_popup_left.Date_Selected_Input) , ColorValue("#ffffff") , 
If( 
    comp_popup_left.Date_Selected_Input = ThisItem.Value ,  
    ColorValue("#f0f0f0") , 
    Color.White
))

If( Month(ThisItem.Value) <> _comp_selected_month , ColorValue("#959595") , 
If( _comp_selected_date = ThisItem.Value , ColorValue("#ffffff") , 
If( ThisItem.Value  = Today(),  ColorValue("#ffffff"),
If( Weekday(ThisItem.Value) = 1  , ColorValue("#ef497f") , 
If( Weekday(ThisItem.Value) = 7  , ColorValue("#3a86ff") , 
Color.Black 
)))))

If( Month(ThisItem.Value) <> _comp_selected_month , Color.Transparent , 
If( _comp_selected_date = ThisItem.Value , ColorValue("#f65810") , 
If( ThisItem.Value  = Today(), ColorValue("#00514a") , 
Color.Transparent)))
